&lt;li&gt;Work cohesively as a unit to accomplish all Life Link III assignments including patient transfers &amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Responsible for maintaining qualifications as required in CFRs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proactively pursues professional growth and supports the learning and development of others&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
